adapter.name: da_CMD_SPLN_ReviewAllREQs
adapter.sqlQuery: With PivotedDetails As ( Select ENTITY, FLOW, SCENARIO, MAX(Case When ACCOUNT = 'REQ_TITLE' THEN TEXT END) AS 'Requirement Title', MAX(Case When ACCOUNT = 'REQ_RQMT_STATUS' THEN TEXT END) AS 'Status' From DATAATTACHMENT Join (VALUES ('a97ad')) AS ENTITY_LIST(VALUE) ON DATAATTACHMENT.ENTITY = ENTITY_LIST.VALUE Where CUBE = 'AFC' And SCENARIO = 'BUD_C2024' And DATAATTACHMENT.ACCOUNT = 'REQ_RQMT_STATUS' Group By ENTITY, FLOW, SCENARIO ), ScenarioID As ( Select MEMBERID From MEMBER Where NAME = 'BUD_C2024' AND DIMTYPEID = 2 ), FilteredDataRecords As ( Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Total_Phased_Obligation_2024' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2024 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 63963222 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Total_Phased_Commitment_2024' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2024 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 63963223 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Phased_Obligation_UFR_2024' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2024 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 73400587 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Phased_Commitment_UFR_2024' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2024 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 73400588 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Total_Phased_Obligation_2025' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2025 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 63963222 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Total_Phased_Commitment_2025' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2025 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 63963223 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Phased_Obligation_UFR_2025' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2025 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 73400587 UNION ALL Select ENTITYID, FLOWID, UD1ID, UD2ID, UD3ID, UD5ID, UD6ID, M12VALUE, 'Phased_Commitment_UFR_2025' AS Type, SCENARIOID From DATARECORD2025 Where SCENARIOID = (Select MEMBERID From ScenarioID) and ACCOUNTID = 73400588 ) Select CONCAT(pd.ENTITY, ':', pd.FLOW) AS ENTITYFLOW, pd.ENTITY, pd.FLOW, pd.SCENARIO, m_ud1.NAME As APPN, m_ud2.NAME As MDEP, m_ud3.NAME As 'APE(9)', m_ud5.NAME As CType, m_ud6.NAME As 'Commitment Item', pd.[Requirement Title], pd.Status, MAX(Case When Type = 'Total_Phased_Obligation_2024' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2024_Total_Phased_Obligation', MAX(Case When Type = 'Total_Phased_Commitment_2024' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2024_Total_Phased_Commitment', MAX(Case When Type = 'Phased_Obligation_UFR_2024' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2024_Phased_Obligation_UFR', MAX(Case When Type = 'Phased_Commitment_UFR_2024' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2024_Phased_Commitment_UFR', MAX(Case When Type = 'Total_Phased_Obligation_2025' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2025_Total_Phased_Obligation', MAX(Case When Type = 'Total_Phased_Commitment_2025' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2025_Total_Phased_Commitment', MAX(Case When Type = 'Phased_Obligation_UFR_2025' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2025_Phased_Obligation_UFR', MAX(Case When Type = 'Phased_Commitment_UFR_2025' THEN M12VALUE END) AS '2025_Phased_Commitment_UFR' From PivotedDetails pd LEFT Join MEMBER m_Entity On pd.ENTITY= m_ENTITY.NAME LEFT Join MEMBER m_Scenario On pd.SCENARIO = m_Scenario.NAME LEFT Join MEMBER m_Flow On pd.FLOW= m_FLOW.NAME LEFT Join FilteredDataRecords A On m_ENTITY.memberID= A.ENTITYID And m_FLOW.memberID= A.FLOWID And A.SCENARIOID = m_Scenario.memberID LEFT Join MEMBER m_ud1 On A.UD1ID = m_ud1.memberId LEFT Join MEMBER m_ud2 On A.UD2ID = m_ud2.memberId LEFT Join MEMBER m_ud3 On A.UD3ID = m_ud3.memberId LEFT Join MEMBER m_ud5 On A.UD5ID = m_ud5.memberId LEFT Join MEMBER m_ud6 On A.UD6ID = m_ud6.memberId Group By pd.ENTITY, pd.FLOW, m_Flow.memberId, pd.SCENARIO, m_ud1.NAME, m_ud2.NAME, m_ud3.NAME, m_ud5.NAME, m_ud6.NAME, pd.[Requirement Title], pd.Status Order By m_Flow.memberId
